rComments: Professor Girard was a pretty good prof. Make sure to go to his lectures or else you will miss a lot of information. His lectures are pretty boring but his exams are pretty easy.

Most people don't take this course for fun, but his sense of humour, passion, & profoundness makes it enjoyable. No textbook! Uploads all readings online for free. They are long and confusing but he's great at breaking them down in class. Attendance not mandatory, but I would not have understood the concepts had I only read the slides. Great prof!!
